com.alexkasko.unsafe.offheapstruct

Class OffHeapStructParallelSorterWithComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.alexkasko.unsafe.offheapstruct.OffHeapStructParallelSorterWithComparator

  •  class OffHeapStructParallelSorterWithComparator
extends Object
    Naive parallel quicksort implementation on top of OffHeapStructSorterWithComparator. Collections is divided in equal parts, each part being sorted separately using user-specified ExecutorService and sorted Iterator is opened over the collection and returned to client. Note: collection will be left in partially sorted state after iterator opening.
